extendedInfo.description: The BOQ launch pad for Android will give you easy access to:-  Mobile Banking-  The BOQ mobile website-  Locate a BOQ branch or ATM-  The BOQ full website-  Call BOQ for help and enquiriesBOQ Mobile banking lets you bank from the convenience of your mobile device. Mobile banking is synchronised with Internet Banking, so your existing payees and billers are already available. Pending authorisations,including payments can also be completed via Mobile banking.If you are registered for Internet banking you can get started with Mobile banking using your existing log on details.Mobile Banking features:-  Balance and transaction history search-  Transfers-  Pay bills with BPAYÂ®-  Pay Anyone payments-  Existing Internet banking daily limits packages for BPAY and Pay Anyone-  Extra online security with the BOQ Security Token-  Payments file upload authorisation-  Direct Debit and Multi Payments authorisation-  Multi user transaction authorisation and privilege delegationLocate a branch or ATM features:-  GPS search for nearest BOQ branches and ATMs Suburb locator-  ATM functionality (ie. withdrawals, deposits etc).-  Managers name, contact details, BSB and operating hours for Branches-  Integration into Google MapsNormal data charges apply. Please refer to your mobile service provider for further details.
